## ğŸ”§ Usage: App Integration

### Wrap the app with CartProvider (optional global state)

```jsx
import { CartProvider } from "./modules/cart/context/CartProvider";

<BrowserRouter>
  <CartProvider>
    <App />
  </CartProvider>
</BrowserRouter>
```



